=====================================
Creating a Matrix View from a C-Array                                   [TOC]
=====================================

If you have a plain C-array you can create a matrix-view that references this
C-array.  By this you can wrap the C-array in a FLENS matrix.  The same trick
allows interfacing FLENS with other numerical libraries.

